<emphasis id="B96D861CFFB7F75FFF6DFB7F0810FAE3" bold="true" box="[189,303,1254,1280]" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Remarks</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BA65A0EFFB7F75FFF6DFA8C0DB6F905" blockId="2.[189,1399,1301,1766]" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">
<bibRefCitation id="EF8827FFFFB7F75FFF6DFA8C08ACFAD3" author="Lallemand V." box="[189,403,1301,1328]" pageId="2" pageNumber="37" refId="ref9050" refString="Lallemand V. 1963. Revision des Fulgoridae (Homoptera). Deuxieme partie. Faunes asiatique et australienne. Memoires de l'Institut royal des Sciences naturelles de Belgique (2 e serie) 75. Institut royal des Sciences naturelles de Belgique, Brussels." type="book" year="1963">Lallemand (1963)</bibRefCitation>
established the tribe 
<taxonomicName id="4C19218DFFB7F75FFD48FA8C0A35FACC" authorityName="Lallemand" authorityYear="1963" box="[664,778,1301,1327]" class="Insecta" family="Fulgoridae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="37" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="tribe" tribe="Limoisini">Limoisini</taxonomicName>
belonging to the subfamily 
<taxonomicName id="4C19218DFFB7F75FFBB0FA8C09C7FAB7" authority="Blanchard, 1847" authorityName="Blanchard" authorityYear="1847" class="Insecta" family="Fulgoridae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="37" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subFamily" subFamily="Aphaeninae">Aphaeninae Blanchard, 1847</taxonomicName>
and assigned 
<taxonomicName id="4C19218DFFB7F75FFE7FFAA308C0FAB0" authorityName="Stal" authorityYear="1863" box="[431,511,1338,1363]" class="Insecta" family="Fulgoridae" genus="Limois" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="37" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B96D861CFFB7F75FFE7FFAA308C0FAB0" box="[431,511,1338,1363]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Limois</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, together with four other genera (
<taxonomicName id="4C19218DFFB7F75FFC7FFAA30C1FFAB7" authority="Lallemand, 1963" authorityName="Lallemand" authorityYear="1963" box="[943,1312,1338,1364]" class="Insecta" family="Fulgoridae" genus="Bloeteanella" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="37" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B96D861CFFB7F75FFC7FFAA30D7CFAB7" box="[943,1091,1338,1364]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Bloeteanella</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EF8827FFFFB7F75FFB81FAA30C1FFAB7" author="Lallemand V." box="[1105,1312,1338,1364]" pageId="2" pageNumber="37" refId="ref9050" refString="Lallemand V. 1963. Revision des Fulgoridae (Homoptera). Deuxieme partie. Faunes asiatique et australienne. Memoires de l'Institut royal des Sciences naturelles de Belgique (2 e serie) 75. Institut royal des Sciences naturelles de Belgique, Brussels." type="book" year="1963">Lallemand, 1963</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C19218DFFB7F75FFAE2FAA30860FA9B" authority="Distant, 1906" authorityName="Distant" authorityYear="1906" class="Insecta" family="Fulgoridae" genus="Erilla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="37" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B96D861CFFB7F75FFAE2FAA30C49FAB7" box="[1330,1398,1338,1364]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Erilla</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EF8827FFFFB7F75FFF6DFAC70860FA9B" author="Distant W. L." box="[189,351,1374,1400]" pageId="2" pageNumber="37" refId="ref8702" refString="Distant W. L. 1906. The Fauna of British India, including Ceylon and Burma. Rhynchota. Vol. 3: Heteroptera-Homoptera. Taylor &amp; Francis, London." type="book" year="1906">Distant, 1906</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C19218DFFB7F75FFEBEFAC70B85FA9B" authority="Lallemand, 1963" authorityName="Lallemand" authorityYear="1963" box="[366,698,1374,1400]" class="Insecta" family="Fulgoridae" genus="Hellerides" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="37" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B96D861CFFB7F75FFEBEFAC708D7FA9B" box="[366,488,1374,1400]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Hellerides</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EF8827FFFFB7F75FFE21FAC70B85FA9B" author="Lallemand V." box="[497,698,1374,1400]" pageId="2" pageNumber="37" refId="ref9050" refString="Lallemand V. 1963. Revision des Fulgoridae (Homoptera). Deuxieme partie. Faunes asiatique et australienne. Memoires de l'Institut royal des Sciences naturelles de Belgique (2 e serie) 75. Institut royal des Sciences naturelles de Belgique, Brussels." type="book" year="1963">Lallemand, 1963</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
which was synonymized with 
<taxonomicName id="4C19218DFFB7F75FFBFEFAC70C6FFA9A" authority="Fennah, 1955" authorityName="Fennah" authorityYear="1955" box="[1070,1360,1374,1401]" class="Insecta" family="Lophopidae" genus="Zophiuma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="37" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B96D861CFFB7F75FFBFEFAC70D9AFA9B" box="[1070,1189,1374,1400]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Zophiuma</emphasis>
Fennah, 1955
</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation id="EF8827FFFFB7F75FFF6DFA1A0866FA7E" author="Liang A. P." box="[189,345,1410,1437]" pageId="2" pageNumber="37" pagination="162 - 164" refId="ref9096" refString="Liang A. P. 1995. Taxonomic change in Oriental Fulgoroidea (Hemiptera: Fulgoromorpha). Journal of the New York Entomological Society 103 (2): 162 - 164." type="journal article" year="1995">Liang (1995)</bibRefCitation>
in the family 
<taxonomicName id="4C19218DFFB7F75FFDD6FA1A0BAAFA7E" authorityName="Stal" authorityYear="1866" box="[518,661,1411,1437]" class="Insecta" family="Lophopidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="37" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Lophopidae</taxonomicName>
, and 
<taxonomicName id="4C19218DFFB7F75FFD06FA1A0D5BFA7D" authority="Lallemand, 1963" authorityName="Lallemand" authorityYear="1963" box="[726,1124,1411,1438]" class="Insecta" family="Fulgoridae" genus="Neolieftinckana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="37" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B96D861CFFB7F75FFD06FA1A0AAFFA7E" box="[726,912,1411,1437]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Neolieftinckana</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EF8827FFFFB7F75FFC4AFA1A0D5BFA7D" author="Lallemand V." box="[922,1124,1411,1438]" pageId="2" pageNumber="37" refId="ref9050" refString="Lallemand V. 1963. Revision des Fulgoridae (Homoptera). Deuxieme partie. Faunes asiatique et australienne. Memoires de l'Institut royal des Sciences naturelles de Belgique (2 e serie) 75. Institut royal des Sciences naturelles de Belgique, Brussels." type="book" year="1963">Lallemand, 1963</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
) to this tribe. 
<bibRefCitation id="EF8827FFFFB7F75FFAC0FA1A0860FA21" author="Nagai S. &amp; Porion T." pageId="2" pageNumber="37" refId="ref9219" refString="Nagai S. &amp; Porion T. 1996. Fulgoridae 2. Illustrated Catalogue of the Asian and Australian Fauna. Sciences Nat, Venette." type="book" year="1996">Nagai &amp; Porion (1996)</bibRefCitation>
recorded seven genera (
<taxonomicName id="4C19218DFFB7F75FFDA5FA3E0A36FA22" authorityName="Lallemand" authorityYear="1963" box="[629,777,1447,1473]" class="Insecta" family="Fulgoridae" genus="Bloeteanella" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="37" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B96D861CFFB7F75FFDA5FA3E0A36FA22" box="[629,777,1447,1473]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Bloeteanella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C19218DFFB7F75FFCC6FA3E0A65FA22" authorityName="Distant" authorityYear="1906" box="[790,858,1447,1473]" class="Insecta" family="Fulgoridae" genus="Erilla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="37" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B96D861CFFB7F75FFCC6FA3E0A65FA22" box="[790,858,1447,1473]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Erilla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C19218DFFB7F75FFCB7FA310A88FA22" authorityName="Stal" authorityYear="1863" box="[871,951,1448,1473]" class="Insecta" family="Fulgoridae" genus="Limois" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="37" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B96D861CFFB7F75FFCB7FA310A88FA22" box="[871,951,1448,1473]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Limois</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C19218DFFB7F75FFC13FA3E0D42FA22" authorityName="Lallemand" authorityYear="1963" box="[963,1149,1447,1473]" class="Insecta" family="Fulgoridae" genus="Neolieftinckana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="37" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B96D861CFFB7F75FFC13FA3E0D42FA22" box="[963,1149,1447,1473]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Neolieftinckana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C19218DFFB7F75FFB59FA310C4EFA22" authority="Fennah, 1977" authorityName="Fennah" authorityYear="1977" box="[1161,1393,1447,1473]" class="Insecta" family="Fulgoridae" genus="Nisax" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="37" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B96D861CFFB7F75FFB59FA310DF3FA22" box="[1161,1228,1448,1473]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Nisax</emphasis>
Fennah, 1977
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C19218DFFB7F75FFF6DFA5508F9FA05" authority="Fennah, 1977" authorityName="Fennah" authorityYear="1977" box="[189,454,1484,1510]" class="Insecta" family="Fulgoridae" genus="Saramel" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="37" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B96D861CFFB7F75FFF6DFA550820FA05" box="[189,287,1484,1510]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Saramel</emphasis>
Fennah, 1977
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C19218DFFB7F75FFE2EFA550BC7FA05" authority="Fennah, 1977" authorityName="Fennah" authorityYear="1977" box="[510,760,1484,1510]" class="Insecta" family="Fulgoridae" genus="Ombro" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="37" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B96D861CFFB7F75FFE2EFA550B6FFA05" box="[510,592,1484,1510]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Ombro</emphasis>
Fennah, 1977
</taxonomicName>
) in 
<taxonomicName id="4C19218DFFB7F75FFCF6FA550AA3FA05" authorityName="Lallemand" authorityYear="1963" box="[806,924,1484,1510]" class="Insecta" family="Fulgoridae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="58" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="tribe" tribe="Limoisini">Limoisini</taxonomicName>
. The genus 
<taxonomicName id="4C19218DFFB7F75FFBF6FA550D49FA06" authorityName="Stal" authorityYear="1863" box="[1062,1142,1484,1509]" class="Insecta" family="Fulgoridae" genus="Limois" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="37" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B96D861CFFB7F75FFBF6FA550D49FA06" box="[1062,1142,1484,1509]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Limois</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
differs from the other six genera in the tribe by the hindwings bicolored (red or yellow in basal part and hyaline apically) rather than concolorous over entire length. 
<taxonomicName id="4C19218DFFB7F75FFDBBF98C0B84F9CD" authorityName="Stal" authorityYear="1863" box="[619,699,1557,1582]" class="Insecta" family="Fulgoridae" genus="Limois" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="37" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B96D861CFFB7F75FFDBBF98C0B84F9CD" box="[619,699,1557,1582]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Limois</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
also differs from 
<taxonomicName id="4C19218DFFB7F75FFC5BF98C0D7AF9CC" authorityName="Lallemand" authorityYear="1963" box="[907,1093,1557,1583]" class="Insecta" family="Fulgoridae" genus="Neolieftinckana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="37" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B96D861CFFB7F75FFC5BF98C0D7AF9CC" box="[907,1093,1557,1583]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Neolieftinckana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by the tegmina hyaline in apical half (entirely opaque in 
<taxonomicName id="4C19218DFFB7F75FFDCDF9A00BE8F9B0" authorityName="Lallemand" authorityYear="1963" box="[541,727,1593,1619]" class="Insecta" family="Fulgoridae" genus="Neolieftinckana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="37" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B96D861CFFB7F75FFDCDF9A00BE8F9B0" box="[541,727,1593,1619]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Neolieftinckana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
). From 
<taxonomicName id="4C19218DFFB7F75FFCE3F9A00ABAF9B0" authorityName="Fennah" authorityYear="1977" box="[819,901,1593,1619]" class="Insecta" family="Fulgoridae" genus="Ombro" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="37" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B96D861CFFB7F75FFCE3F9A00ABAF9B0" box="[819,901,1593,1619]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Ombro</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
it differs by the phallobase having 4 paired lobes (with 5 paired lobes in 
<taxonomicName id="4C19218DFFB7F75FFDC2F9C40B5BF994" authorityName="Fennah" authorityYear="1977" box="[530,612,1629,1655]" class="Insecta" family="Fulgoridae" genus="Ombro" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="37" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B96D861CFFB7F75FFDC2F9C40B5BF994" box="[530,612,1629,1655]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Ombro</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
). From 
<taxonomicName id="4C19218DFFB7F75FFD13F9C40A38F994" authorityName="Distant" authorityYear="1906" box="[707,775,1629,1655]" class="Insecta" family="Fulgoridae" genus="Erilla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="37" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B96D861CFFB7F75FFD13F9C40A38F994" box="[707,775,1629,1655]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Erilla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C19218DFFB7F75FFC91F9C70ABBF994" authorityName="Fennah" authorityYear="1977" box="[833,900,1630,1655]" class="Insecta" family="Fulgoridae" genus="Nisax" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="37" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B96D861CFFB7F75FFC91F9C70ABBF994" box="[833,900,1630,1655]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Nisax</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
it differs by the cephalic process of vertex slanting upwards to backwards, flattened on the vertex (cephalic process of vertex reduced in 
<taxonomicName id="4C19218DFFB7F75FFAD1F91B0C7AF97F" authorityName="Distant" authorityYear="1906" box="[1281,1349,1666,1692]" class="Insecta" family="Fulgoridae" genus="Erilla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="37" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B96D861CFFB7F75FFAD1F91B0C7AF97F" box="[1281,1349,1666,1692]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Erilla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and forming a granular mass in middle of vertex in 
<taxonomicName id="4C19218DFFB7F75FFD3AF93E0A12F923" authorityName="Fennah" authorityYear="1977" box="[746,813,1703,1728]" class="Insecta" family="Fulgoridae" genus="Nisax" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="37" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B96D861CFFB7F75FFD3AF93E0A12F923" box="[746,813,1703,1728]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Nisax</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
). From 
<taxonomicName id="4C19218DFFB7F75FFC5CF93F0D1FF923" authorityName="Lallemand" authorityYear="1963" box="[908,1056,1702,1728]" class="Insecta" family="Fulgoridae" genus="Bloeteanella" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="37" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B96D861CFFB7F75FFC5CF93F0D1FF923" box="[908,1056,1702,1728]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Bloeteanella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
it differs by the frons having 2 or 3 smooth longitudinal carinae (wrinkled and grooved carinae in 
<taxonomicName id="4C19218DFFB7F75FFC34F9520D47F906" authorityName="Lallemand" authorityYear="1963" box="[996,1144,1739,1765]" class="Insecta" family="Fulgoridae" genus="Bloeteanella" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="37" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B96D861CFFB7F75FFC34F9520D47F906" box="[996,1144,1739,1765]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Bloeteanella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
).
</paragraph>
